r>\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\"|'''[[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]'''\n| <center>3\u20130</center>\n| [[KK Cibona|Cibona]]\n| [[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]\n| <center>13\u20131</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2016\u201317 A-1 League|2016\u201317]]</center>\n| [[KK Cibona|Cibona]]\n| <center>2\u20133</center>\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\"|'''[[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]'''\n| [[GKK \u0160ibenik|\u0160ibenik]]\n| <center>21\u20135</center>\n|- \n| <center>[[2017\u201318 A-1 League|2017\u201318]]</center>\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\"| '''[[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]'''\n| <center>3\u20131</center>\n| [[KK Cibona|Cibona]]\n| [[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]\n| <center>23\u20131</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2018\u201319 Premijer liga|2018\u201319]]</center>\n| style=\"background:#ff9;\"|'''[[KK Cibona|Cibona]]'''\n| <center>4\u20130</center>\n| [[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]\n| [[KK Zadar|Zadar]]\n| <center>18\u20134</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2019\u201320 Hrvatski telekom Premijer liga|2019\u201320]]</center>\n| colspan=5 style=\"background:#eaecef;\"| '''Season canceled''' due to the [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Croatia|Coronavirus pandemic]]\n|}\n\n===By club===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:50%;\"| Club\n!W\n!L\n!Total\n|-\n| [[KK Cibona|Cibona]]\n| <center>19</center>\n| <center>7</center>\n| <center>'''26'''</center>\n|-\n| [[KK Cedevita|Cedevita]]\n| <center>5</center>\n| <center>3</center>\n| <center>'''8'''</center>\n|-\n| [[KK Zadar|Zadar]]\n| <center>2</center>\n| <center>11</center>\n| <center>'''13'''</center>\n|-\n| [[KK Split|Split]]\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>6</center>\n| <center>'''7'''</center>\n|-\n| [[KK Zagreb|Zagreb]]\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>0</center>\n| <center>'''1'''</center>\n|-\n| [[KK Zrinjevac|Zrinjevac]]\n| <center>0</center>\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>'''1'''</center>\n|}\n\n==Croatian basketball clubs in European and worldwide competitions==\n{{main|Croatian basketball clubs in European and worldwide competitions}}\n\n==See also==\n