]], [[Christchurch]]\n|align=center|18\u20133\n|-\n|15 August\n|[[Carisbrook]], [[Dunedin]]\n|align=center|14\u20139\n|-\n|rowspan=3 |{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[1962 Australia rugby union tour of New Zealand|1962]]\n|22 September\n|[[Eden Park]], [[Auckland]]\n|rowspan=3 align=right|{{ru-rt|New Zealand}}\n|align=center|16\u20138\n|rowspan=3|{{ru|Australia}}\n|rowspan=3|{{flagicon|New Zealand|size=50px}}\n|-\n|8 September\n|[[Carisbrook]], [[Dunedin]]\n|align=center|3\u20130\n|-\n|25 August\n|[[Athletic Park, Wellington|Athletic Park]], [[Wellington]]\n|align=center|9\u20139\n|-\n|rowspan=2|{{flagicon|Australia}} [[1962 New Zealand rugby union tour of Australia|1962]]\n|4 June\n|[[Sydney Cricket Ground|SCG]], [[Sydney]]\n|rowspan=2 align=right|{{ru-rt|Australia}}\n|align=center|5\u201314\n|rowspan=2|{{ru|New Zealand}}\n|rowspan=2|{{flagicon|New Zealand|size=50px}}\n|-\n|26 May\n|[[Brisbane Showgrounds|Exhibition Ground]], [[Brisbane]]\n|align=center|6\u201320\n|-\n|rowspan=3 |{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[1958 Australia rugby union tour of New Zealand|1958]]\n|20 September\n|[[Epsom, New Zealand|Epsom Showgrounds]], [[Auckland]]\n|rowspan=3 align=right|{{ru-rt|New Zealand}}\n|align=center|17\u20138\n|rowspan=3|{{ru|Australia}}\n|rowspan=3|{{flagicon|New Zealand|size=50px}}\n|-\n|6 September\n|[[Lancaster Park]], [[Christchurch]]\n|align=center|3\u20136\n|-\n|23 August\n|[[Athletic Park, Wellington|Athletic Park]], [[Wellington]]\n|align=center|25\u20133\n|-\n|rowspan=2|{{flagicon|Australia}} [[1957 New Zealand rugby union tour of Australia|1957]]\n|1 June\n|[[Brisbane Showgrounds|Exhibition Ground]], [[Brisbane]]\n|rowspan=2 align=right|{{ru-rt|Australia}}\n|align=center|9\u201322\n|rowspan=2|{{ru|New Zealand}}\n|rowspan=2|{{flagicon|New Zealand|size=50px}}\n|-\n|25 May\n|[[Sydney Cricket Ground|SCG]], [[Sydney]]\n|align=center|11\u201325\n|-\n|rowspan=3 |{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[1955 Australia rugby union tour of New Zealand|1955]]\n|17 September\n|[[Eden Park]], [[A