tober 2013}}\n\n==Gallery==\n<center>\n<gallery widths=\"90\" heights=\"120px\" perrow=\"6\" style=\"border: 5px solid #a86; box-shadow: 0.1em 0.1em 0.5em rgba(0,0,0,0.75); border-radius: 0.5em;\">\nImage:Kezdi centre1.JPG|City center\nImage:Kezdi centre2.JPG|City center\nImage:Kezdi centre8.jpg|Cultural Center\nFile:Children inside Sala Polivalenta Sportsarnok.jpg|Children inside Sala Polivalenta Sporting Hall\nFile:Autonomy of Sz\u00e9kely Land - Day of Sz\u00e9kely Freedom 2013.03.10 (18).JPG|Day of Sz\u00e9kely Freedom Celebration\n</gallery>\n</center>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|T\u00e2rgu Secuiesc}}\n* [http://www.kezdi.ro/ Official site] {{in lang|hu|ro|en}}\n* [https://www.kezdi.info/centrum K\u00e9zdiv\u00e1s\u00e1rhely Centrum City Map]\n* [http://www.kezdise.com Official site of the K\u00e9zdiv\u00e1s\u00e1rhely Sportclub (KSE)] {{in lang|hu|en}} \n* [http://www.nmg.ro/ Nagy M\u00f3zes High School]\n* [http://www.gaboraron.ro/ G\u00e1bor Aron High School]\n\n{{Covasna County}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Targu Secuiesc}}\n[[Category:Populated places in Covasna County]]\n[[Category:Cities in Romania]]\n[[Category:Market towns in Transylvania]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Romanian subdivision\n|type                   = municipality\n|county                 = Covasna\n|population_total       = auto\n|map_caption            = Location in Covasna County\n|subdivisions           = \n| official_name=T\u00e2rgu Secuiesc\n|other_name= K\u00e9zdiv\u00e1s\u00e1rhely\n| image_skyline          = {{Photomontage\n  | photo1a = Kezdi_centre3.JPG{{!}}\n  | photo1b = Vigad\u00f3 (K\u00e9zdiv\u00e1s\u00e1rhely).jpg{{!}}\n  | photo2a = Kezdi6.JPG{{!}}\n  | photo2b = Kezdi3.JPG{{!}}\n  | photo3a = Kezdi eglise.JPG{{!}}\n  | photo3b = Gaboaronagyuja.jpg{{!}}\n  | spacing = 0\n  | position = center\n  | color_border = white\n  | color = white\n  | size = 270\n  | foot_montage = Descending, from top: Centre of T\u00e2rgu Secuiesc, Concert Hall, 